---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Hafiz
  Translator: Daniel Ladinsky
  Author: Hafiz
  ISBN: 978-0143117544
  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Dropping Keys
Description: December 27
---
The small man builds cages for everyone he knows,

while the sage, who has to duck his head when the moon is low,

keeps dropping keys all night long for the beautiful, rowdy prisoners.
